{"id":"18c135efad78aaedefab9472e4014f3db0ba47532d302145","commits":["d2433b23e9050dcb3aeb6b36042c770b30fac741"],"user_facing":true,"description":"**Cloning from the default profile now works.** The profile wizard's clone-from-default option previously produced an empty-base profile (and falsely reported its settings source); it now clones the real ~/.claude settings.","type":"fix"}
{"id":"18c135f97286111a9a2f56668e6346478f408d81fae92bf9","commits":["a771f9bd0c1a3fe0747f5ffc0573a9196e7e6e88"],"user_facing":true,"description":"**Health no longer claims inode cleanup it could not persist.** On read-only workspaces the inode check now reports that stale entries were found but not persisted, instead of 'cleaned'.","type":"fix"}
